{"repo": "ForensicArtifacts/artifacts", "pull_number": 649, "instance_id": "ForensicArtifacts__artifacts-649", "issue_numbers": [647], "base_commit": "3c89139caf11a2ffed4ee60f16a7e38839cd4f23", "patch": "diff --git a/artifacts/data/webbrowser.yaml b/artifacts/data/webbrowser.yaml\nindex 7d5422d6..957b9195 100644\n--- a/artifacts/data/webbrowser.yaml\n+++ b/artifacts/data/webbrowser.yaml\n@@ -1293,7 +1293,7 @@ sources:\n     - '%%users.localappdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite'\n     - '%%users.localappdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite-wal'\n     - '%%users.appdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite'\n-    - '%%users.localappdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite-wal'\n+    - '%%users.appdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite-wal'\n     separator: '\\'\n   supported_os: [Windows]\n supported_os: [Darwin, Linux, Windows]\n", "test_patch": "", "problem_statement": "Incorrect firefox places.sqlite-wal path\nHi, first off - thanks for all your work in this amazing repo.\n\nI noticed that there is a duplicate in Mozilla firefox places. Because of this, the default location of the roaming appdata places.sqlite-wal is not listed.\n\nThe current paths looks like this (from https://github.com/ForensicArtifacts/artifacts/blob/main/artifacts/data/webbrowser.yaml#L1290).\n\n```\n- type: FILE\n  attributes:\n    paths:\n    - '%%users.localappdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite'\n    - '%%users.localappdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite-wal'\n    - '%%users.appdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite'\n    - '%%users.localappdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite-wal'\n    separator: '\\'\n  supported_os: [Windows]\n```\n\nI believe the corrected paths should be as below:\n\n```\n- type: FILE\n  attributes:\n    paths:\n    - '%%users.localappdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite'\n    - '%%users.localappdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite-wal'\n    - '%%users.appdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite'\n    - '%%users.appdata%%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\\*\\places.sqlite-wal'\n    separator: '\\'\n  supported_os: [Windows]\n```\nChanged line is https://github.com/ForensicArtifacts/artifacts/blob/main/artifacts/data/webbrowser.yaml#L1296\n\n", "hints_text": "\n\n", "all_hints_text": "\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/ForensicArtifacts/artifacts/commit/74c416d6033a130d4204d13012c2c0cbe6d58ec3"], "created_at": "2025-11-20T16:01:24Z"}
